# Separate accounts for door devices(firmware) and the controlling entity (gateway)
# Primarily to limit compromise to single unit if a firmware device is compromised
user dlock-firmware
write fbp
read doors/+/lock
read doors/+/unlock
write doors/+/error
write doors/+/islocked

user dlock-gateway
read fbp
readwrite doors/+/lock
readwrite doors/+/unlock
read doors/+/error
read doors/+/islocked
